All Classes

Class Description
Configuration
Configuration file parser.
Direction
A general purpose enumeration for representing the direction an entity is moving along a TrainRoute.
Location
Generic positional information for an entity
Logger
Logger utility.
PairedLimit
Utility construct for a pair of corresponding minimum and maximum limits for a parameter.
Passenger
Representation of an individual who will travel via train between origin and destination stations.
RouteSpecification
Utility construct for Route specifications.
RouteStyle
Route styles (linear/point-to-point and circular)
Station
Representation of a station on a train route.
Train
Representation of a train on a train route.
TrainRoute
Representation of a train route consisting of a pair of parallel tracks, Station(s) at fixed locations along the tracks, and Train(s) that move along the tracks.
TrainSimulation
A fully parameterized, synchronous, single-threaded train simulation.
TrainSpecification
Utility construct for Train specifications.
